        "---\n",
        "## 🆓 Free LLM Backup — llm7.io API\n",
        "\n",
        "When `USE_FREE_LLM = True`, the system routes LLM calls through\n",
        "**[llm7.io](https://llm7.io)** — a free, OpenAI-compatible inference gateway.\n",
        "\n",
        "| Property | Value |\n",
        "|----------|-------|\n",
        "| **Endpoint** | `https://api.llm7.io/v1` |\n",
        "| **API Key** | Any non-empty string (no account needed) |\n",
        "| **Compatible with** | `langchain_openai.ChatOpenAI` via `base_url` |\n",
        "| **Model used** | `gpt-4o` (proxied) |\n",
        "| **Retrieval** | BM25 (no embeddings required) |\n",
        "| **Use case** | Development, demos, offline-friendly CI |\n",
        "\n",
        "> **Note:** llm7.io is used only as a **backup** for free-tier access.\n",
        "> The primary production path (`USE_OPENAI = True`) uses your own OpenAI key\n",
        "> with Chroma vector storage and is preserved for later phases.\n",
        "\n",
        "### Mode Priority\n",
        "```\n",
        "USE_OPENAI = True   →  OpenAI GPT-4o-mini + Chroma  (primary / production)\n",
        "USE_FREE_LLM = True →  llm7.io  + BM25              (backup / development)\n",
        "Both False          →  Pure BM25 offline             (no LLM, rule-based only)\n",
        "```\n"
