        "---\n",
        "## 📚 Section 1 — RAG Integration & Knowledge Management\n",
        "\n",
        "### How Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) works in this system\n",
        "\n",
        "```\n",
        "Policy Documents (.md / .pdf)\n",
        "        │\n",
        "        ▼\n",
        " ┌─────────────────┐\n",
        " │  Text Splitter  │  Splits docs into overlapping 500-char chunks\n",
        " └─────────────────┘\n",
        "        │\n",
        "        ▼\n",
        " ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\n",
        " │           Embedding Model               │\n",
        " │  Each chunk → dense vector (e.g. 1536-d │\n",
        " │  for text-embedding-3-large)            │\n",
        " └─────────────────────────────────────────┘\n",
        "        │\n",
        "        ▼\n",
        " ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\n",
        " │         Vector Database (Chroma)        │\n",
        " │  Stores vectors + metadata + raw text   │\n",
        " │  Indexed for fast cosine-similarity     │\n",
        " └─────────────────────────────────────────┘\n",
        "        │  At query time:\n",
        "        ▼\n",
        " ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\n",
        " │     Retriever  (top-k=3 results)        │\n",
        " │  Query → embed → ANN search → chunks   │\n",
        " └─────────────────────────────────────────┘\n",
        "        │\n",
        "        ▼\n",
        " ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐\n",
        " │      Knowledge Agent (LLM + context)    │\n",
        " │  Grounded answer = LLM(query + chunks)  │\n",
        " └─────────────────────────────────────────┘\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "### Embeddings\n",
        "An **embedding** converts a piece of text into a fixed-length numerical vector.\n",
        "Semantically similar texts produce vectors that are close in high-dimensional space\n",
        "(measured by cosine similarity or dot product). This lets us retrieve *meaning* rather\n",
        "than just matching keywords.\n",
        "\n",
        "### Vector Database\n",
        "**Chroma** (when `USE_OPENAI=True`) stores each chunk's vector alongside its raw text\n",
        "and metadata (source filename, title). At retrieval time it performs an\n",
        "**Approximate Nearest-Neighbour (ANN)** search in milliseconds, returning the most\n",
        "semantically relevant chunks regardless of exact wording.\n",
        "\n",
        "### BM25 Fallback\n",
        "When no OpenAI key is set, the system falls back to **BM25** — a classical\n",
        "term-frequency retriever. It is fast and requires no embedding model, making it ideal\n",
        "for offline or cost-free development runs.\n",
        "\n",
        "### Context Grounding\n",
        "Retrieved chunks are injected into the agent's prompt as grounding context,\n",
        "preventing hallucination by anchoring answers strictly to documented policy.\n"
      ],
