      "source": [
        "---\n",
        "## 🤖 Section 3 — Agent Architecture & Role Definition\n",
        "\n",
        "This system uses a **four-agent pipeline** orchestrated by LangGraph.\n",
        "Each agent has a single, well-defined responsibility. Inter-agent collaboration\n",
        "happens through the shared `GraphState` object (a typed Pydantic model passed\n",
        "through every node).\n",
        "\n",
        "```\n",
        "                        ┌─────────────────┐\n",
        "  User Query ──────────▶│  INTAKE AGENT   │  Classifies intent & routes\n",
        "                        └────────┬────────┘\n",
        "              ┌──────────────────┼──────────────────┐\n",
        "              ▼                  ▼                  ▼\n",
        "   ┌──────────────────┐  ┌──────────────────┐  ┌──────────────────┐\n",
        "   │ KNOWLEDGE AGENT  │  │ WORKFLOW AGENT   │  │ ESCALATION AGENT │\n",
        "   │                  │  │                  │  │                  │\n",
        "   │ RAG retrieval    │  │ Calls MCP tools: │  │ Opens ticket via │\n",
        "   │ Policy Q&A       │  │ reset_password   │  │ MCP create_ticket│\n",
        "   │ MFA guidance     │  │ unlock_account   │  │ Notifies IT team │\n",
        "   └──────────────────┘  │ create_ticket    │  └──────────────────┘\n",
        "                         │ log_analysis     │\n",
        "                         └──────────────────┘\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "### Agent Roles\n",
        "\n",
        "| Agent | Trigger Conditions | Outputs |\n",
        "|-------|--------------------|---------|\n",
        "| **Intake** | Every request (entry point) | `Intent` (top_level + label + confidence) |\n",
        "| **Knowledge** | `policy_question`, `mfa_help` | Policy-grounded natural language answer |\n",
        "| **Workflow** | `forgot_password`, `account_locked` | MCP tool results, temp password / unlock status |\n",
        "| **Escalation** | Unclassified intent, tool failures | Support ticket ID, IT handoff message |\n",
        "\n",
        "### State Sharing (Inter-Agent Collaboration)\n",
        "`GraphState` is the shared blackboard — each node reads from it and writes\n",
        "partial updates back. LangGraph merges updates immutably, ensuring no agent\n",
        "can corrupt another's data.\n"
      ],
      "id": "it_um6o-yonG"
    },
