        "---\n",
        "## 🖥️ Section 6 — Professional UI: Keyword-Highlighted Menus\n",
        "\n",
        "The terminal UI uses **ANSI escape codes** to:\n",
        "- Display **colour-highlighted keyword shortcuts** in square brackets\n",
        "- Format responses in clean bordered panels\n",
        "- Show agent routing and MCP tool call summaries after each interaction\n",
        "\n",
        "> **Interaction model:** Instead of typing an exact phrase, the user types any\n",
        "> highlighted keyword — e.g. `sign`, `in`, `login`, `1` all route to Sign-In.\n",
        "> This is shown visually in the menu with coloured `[keyword]` labels.\n"
